# PHProjectJournalEntryElement

**Class**

An element that represents a journal entry within project section content.

## Declaration

```swift
class PHProjectJournalEntryElement
```

## Describing a Journal Entry

- **date**: The date of the journal entry.
- **assetElement**: An optional asset to represent the date in the journal entry.
- **textElement**: Descriptive text for the date of the entry.

## Subclassing Project Elements

- **PHProjectAssetElement**: An element that represents a media asset within project section content.
- **PHProjectTextElement**: An element that represents text within project section content.
- **PHProjectMapElement**: An element that represents a map within project section content.
